      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E_rms or GCI-normalized error) below acceptance threshold for hemolysis index and velocity fields.",
      "rationale": "Normalized RMS error in hemolysis index across all 5 operating points: 8.2%. Velocity field comparison against PIV data yields E_rms = 6.7% of peak velocity. Both within MRL 5 acceptance bounds defined in assessment plan."
