    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed at or above required levels for MRL 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification across all 10 uncertain model inputs demonstrates that the 95th-percentile predicted NIH remains below the absolute clinical hemolysis threshold across all five operating points. Discretization error bounded by GCI below 5%. Validation error within MRL 5 acceptance bounds. The credibility evidence package is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class III VAD device.",
